Kellie Shanygne Williams https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kellie_Shanygne_Williams 0 Kellie Shanygne Williams-Jackson (born March 22, 1976), is an American actress. She is best known for her role as Laura Lee Winslow, the middle child of Carl and Harriette Winslow on the ABC/CBS television series Family Matters which ran from 1989–1998.
